- Ayush M. testimonial is genuine (mom's medicine reminder) — role should be "Mom's Reminder Setter, Indore" not "Founder"

## COMMUNICATION
- Direct, no fluff
- Hinglish OK in user-facing copy
- Show exact code, never pseudo-code
- Plain text answers only, no JSON UI elements
